**Overview**

This playbook defines the scope of responsibilities among teams involved in the Binary-Option workflow. It aims to ensure clear role delineation, well-defined accountability, and enhanced cross-functional collaboration and response efficiency.

**👥 Team Roles and Responsibilities**

🟦 External Tech Team (Primary Contact : @Barry W)

🔹 Primary Responsibility Phases

- UX & UI feature flow  
- Binary-Option flow and handling logic

🔹 Key Responsibilities

- Initialization of order placement workflow  
- Placement mechanism validation  
- Settlement accuracy  
- Wallet freeze/unfreeze handling  
- Service status monitoring and trading flow logging
